        <updateDate>2023-08-25T18:41:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Military Pay Enhancement Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill increases the maximum amounts of certain bonuses and special pay authorities for enlisted members, nuclear officers (naval), officers in a regular or reserve component of a uniformed service who are training for or maintaining designations related to aviation, and members of a regular or reserve component of the uniformed services who serve in a critical career field or skill as designated by the applicable uniformed service.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
